text: Megan Parkes (born 2 March 1993) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2015 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * sa- ladies-water-polo-squad-named-2013 * water-polo-reports-women-day-1 Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
